Technology Stack Summary
Frontend: AWS Amplify, React.js/Streamlit, 3D.js (for molecule visualization).

Compute & Orchestration: AWS Step Functions, AWS Lambda, AWS Batch/Fargate.

AI/ML: Amazon SageMaker (PyTorch/TensorFlow), Amazon OpenSearch Serverless (Vector DB).

Storage: Amazon S3, Amazon DynamoDB.

Infrastructure: AWS CDK (Python/TypeScript) for one-click deployment.
